author: claude-code-agent
acceptance_criteria: "CodeFactor reports 0 unsafe-optional-chaining (\"Optional chaining with invalid undefined usage\") findings; full coverage suite stays green at 100%; pnpm typecheck passes."
parent: pm-92if
resolution: Rewrote unsafe optional-chain assertion dereferences and the CodeFactor no-useless-spread helper.
expected_result: Unsafe optional-chain and no-useless-spread CodeFactor maintainability findings are removed without behavior changes.
actual_result: "Assertions use explicit intermediate values; focused tests, typecheck, static quality, coverage 100/100/100/100, release gates, and temp smoke passed."
